Goto Definition / cmd+click on filename/methodname in mac vscode does not work for salesforce apex : 
Fix : Open settings.json in vscode and add the below line 
   "salesforcedx-vscode-apex.java.home":"/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/zulu-17.jdk/Contents/Home"
    
    
    Make sure the jdk is installed before making above change. 
   
